description:
For those of you who are old enough to remember PaRappa the Rapper for PS1 ^_^

The mod replaces Boyfriend with PaRappa the Rapper in Week 3, Week 4, and Week 6. Both the skin (made by uni_seth) and the vocals (made by Flameout56) are replaced. All the credit goes to those awesome guys.
